WEBVTT

00:00.050 --> 00:04.400
If you're a pet owner, you know how flying can be a rough experience for your dog or cat.

00:04.870 --> 00:08.940
On human airlines, your furry best friend is treated no better than a suitcase,...

00:09.140 --> 00:13.480
...getting stowed away in the uncomfortable and frightening confines of the plane's cargo hold.

00:13.810 --> 00:15.400
Introducing Pet Airways,...

00:15.610 --> 00:20.680
...the world's first airline exclusively dedicated to the safe and comfortable transportation of pets.

00:21.020 --> 00:24.690
At Pet Airways, pets fly in the main cabin, not in cargo.

00:25.060 --> 00:28.600
We believe our pets are not luggage. They're "pawssengers".

00:28.810 --> 00:33.530
On Pet Airways, your best friend travels in four legged style in the main cabin,...

00:33.800 --> 00:40.240
...constantly monitored by a pet attendant with the temperature just right and with lots of fresh circulating air.

00:40.570 --> 00:46.440
Your pet arrives happy and well cared for, and with a lot less stress for both you and your pet.

00:46.910 --> 00:48.680
We should all be so lucky.

00:49.040 --> 00:53.220
Pet Airways, the perfect form of travel for your best friend.

00:53.750 --> 00:56.020
Thank you for visiting PetAirways.com

